# Integration of Supply Chain Security into Cybersecurity & Enterprise Risk Management – Audit Checklist

## 1. Integration into Cybersecurity & ERM Programs
- [ ] Has the organization integrated its supply chain security practices into its overall cybersecurity and enterprise risk management programs?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierte Integration in Cybersecurity- und ERM-Richtlinien
- Nachweis der Governance-Freigabe
- Mapping von Supply Chain Sicherheitspraktiken zu ERM-Prozessen
- Management-Review-Dokumentation

---

## 2. Application of Policies & Controls
- [ ] How are the cybersecurity and enterprise risk management processes, policies, and controls applied to the organization's supply chain and third-party relationships?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierte Prozesse, Policies, und Kontrollen für Lieferanten
- Nachweis der Anwendung auf kritische Supplier/Third Parties
- Integration in Risk Registers oder Dashboards
- Verbindlichkeit in Verträgen oder SLAs dokumentiert

---

## 3. Monitoring & Performance Measurement
- [ ] Does the organization have a defined process to monitor and measure the performance of its supply chain security practices as part of its cybersecurity and enterprise risk management programs?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Monitoring-Prozesse dokumentiert
- KPI/KRI für Supply Chain Security definiert
- Reports an Management oder Board
- Historie von Reviews und Anpassungen

---

## 4. Alignment with Cybersecurity & Risk Objectives
- [ ] Are the supply chain security practices and their performance metrics aligned with the organization's overall cybersecurity and risk management objectives and key performance indicators (KPIs)?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- KPI-Mapping zwischen Supply Chain Security und Unternehmenszielen
- Nachweis der strategischen Abstimmung mit Cybersecurity- und ERM-Zielen
- Management-Review-Dokumentation
- Anpassungen bei Abweichungen

---

## 5. Reflection of Updates & Changes
- [ ] How does the organization ensure that changes or updates to its cybersecurity and enterprise risk management programs are also reflected in its supply chain security practices?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Prozess zur Aktualisierung der Supply Chain Security bei Änderungen dokumentiert
- Änderungsprotokolle und Versionierung
- Nachweis von Management-Freigaben
- Integration in Trainings oder SOPs

---

## 6. Roles & Responsibilities
- [ ] Are there clear roles and responsibilities assigned for the integration and ongoing management of supply chain security practices within the organization's cybersecurity and enterprise risk management programs?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- RACI-Matrix oder Governance-Dokumentation
- Benannte Teams / Personen für Supply Chain Security Management
- Nachweis von Schulungen / Awareness
- Eskalations- und Freigabeprozesse dokumentiert

---

## 7. Continuous Improvement
- [ ] Are there mechanisms in place to review and continuously improve the integration of supply chain security practices into the organization's cybersecurity and enterprise risk management programs?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Review- und Audit-Zyklen dokumentiert
- Lessons Learned und Verbesserungsmaßnahmen nachgewiesen
- KPI-Trendanalysen für Supply Chain Security
- Management-Freigaben für Verbesserungsmaßnahmen

---

## 8. Communication of Performance & Results
- [ ] How does the organization ensure that the performance and results of its supply chain security practices are effectively communicated to relevant stakeholders?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Kommunikationsplan für Supply Chain Security Performance
- Reports, Dashboards oder Management-Meetings nachgewiesen
- Feedback-Schleifen dokumentiert
- Nachweis der Kenntnisnahme durch relevante Stakeholder
